docs {
  ## Get Inventory Adjustment
  ดึงรายละเอียดทั้งหมดของรายการปรับปรุงสินค้าคงคลังเฉพาะรายการ (รับเข้าหรือจ่ายออก) รวมถึงสินค้าที่ได้รับผลกระทบ จำนวน และสาเหตุของการแก้ไข สำหรับการตรวจสอบและยืนยัน

  Retrieves the full details of a specific inventory adjustment (stock-in or stock-out), including affected products, quantities, and the reason for the correction, for audit review and verification.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Inventory Adjustment ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `type` | string | Yes | — | Adjustment type: `stock-in` or `stock-out` |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "type": "stock-in",
      "doc_no": "ADJ-2026-0001",
      "doc_date": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "doc_status": "draft",
      "location_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "location_name": "Main Store",
      "info": [],
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | `type` query parameter is missing or invalid |
  | 404 | Inventory adjustment not found |
}

params:query {
  type: stock-in
}

params:path {
  id: {{inventory_adjustment_id}}
}
